  <brief_title>Efficacy and Safety of V0111 Cream on Open Cracked Heel in Diabetic Patients With Polyneuropathy.</brief_title>
  <sponsors>
    <lead_sponsor>
      <agency>Pierre Fabre Medicament</agency>
      <agency_class>Industry</agency_class>
    </lead_sponsor>
  </sponsors>
  <source>Pierre Fabre Medicament</source>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to evaluate the efficacy and the safety of the cream V0111 in
      the treatment of fissure(s) situated on the heels in diabetic patients with polyneuropathy.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
